<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78849545-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s153"><num value="153">§ 153.</num><heading> Dividends</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Dividends declared by a China Trade Act corporation shall be derived wholly from the surplus profits of its business.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78849546-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1922-09-19/ch346/s13">Sept. 19, 1922, ch. 346, § 13</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/42/853">42 Stat. 853</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
